title: Jesus On E's
info:
Remix of the Jesus On E's soundtrack by Echo. Lyrics:

Ooh yeah! C'mon!

My warped senses tell me
That nothing I see is real.
Saturday tends to betray me
Like a (??? suggester), you see.
The time to wonder ceases:
You'll (??? solely) see
That your religion's based on
Nothing but Jesus on E's.

Slam the door when you're leaving,
So I'll know for sure that you're gone.
??? (will try to compel?)
??? force is set free.

Reality's razors will teach you
That Satan is high on speed,
And LSD will convince thee
That Jesus was whacked on E's!
